<p>Paramedic Laura Heath added: 'Off to the pub today? If anything, be sensible and please don't drink and drive. Working 6-6 today, choose your ride back wisely.'</p>

<p>Dr Tom Leckie, consultant in emergency medicine, at the Royal Oldham Hospital, told the MeN: 'We are asking the public to think carefully before attending A&amp;E this weekend and in the coming weeks.</p>

